 Maya ( meanings=2 glosses=2 NOUN_HUMAN NOUN_FIRSTNAME NOUN_SHE NOUN_ABSTRACT NOUN NOUN_PROPER_SINGULAR COMMON1 KINDERGARTEN ) 
    Mayan_language~1nz (^Indian~1) a family of American Indian languages spoken by Maya
    Mayan~2nz (^Indian~2) a member of an American Indian people of Yucatan and Belize and Guatemala who had a culture characterized by outstanding architecture and pottery and astronomy
